{"tid":1427210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啲人要將港紙變美金 不如搵97年嘅江湖大佬出山","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:36:25.000Z","uid":296674,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab369014a091aac377f5bccc64012cfc0bacd01","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"係我就搵索羅斯幫手啦<br />\n佢九七年個陣爭啲將成個亞太區股市拖冧<br />\n連英倫銀行到打贏過<br />\n真係遇神殺神遇鬼殺鬼<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要好支持民主運動 亦非常反中共<br />\n今年年頭公開話過習大喺「自由開放社會嘅最大威脅」<br />\n<br />\n不如搵佢幫拖 嗌埋佢啲金融大鱷friend<br />\n追擊港幣 狙擊中資<br />\n睇下今次香港俾大陸借晒外匯儲備 仲唔一齊攬炒<br />\n我諗佢老人家等咗呢個moment等咗好耐"},{"pid":"22ffcd10d3d0fe1be1cecce327b879261c09360c","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:21:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"302ed65a273c9296e893dcdd94e71100cd5b2c88","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:21:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"83c05f4a57764d3f5bd41b830513458964844348","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c742eb3bcf74a01367f50f91a81abd354062b6df","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Soros#Views_on_China\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGeorge_Soros%23Views_on_China&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=b27aae45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Soros#Views_on_China</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B9%94%E6%B2%BB%C2%B7%E7%B4%A2%E7%BD%97%E6%96%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B9%2594%25E6%25B2%25BB%25C2%25B7%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E7%25BD%2597%25E6%2596%25AF&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=93b88b9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B9%94%E6%B2%BB%C2%B7%E7%B4%A2%E7%BD%97%E6%96%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n但索羅斯在2019年世界經濟論壇上批評中國「<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">在所有威權國家中，中國是財力最雄厚、最強大的，在人工智慧等高科技方面也最先進，這使得習近平成為開放社會最危險的對手。</span></span>」索羅斯強調，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果威權國家都如此發展下去，會成為極權主義國家。</span></span>他還警告說，中國正試圖在網絡經濟上掌握話語權，並通過其技術和策略在開發中國家中占統治地位。同時還指出「不能讓中興、華為等企業輕易逃脫，而應該嚴厲打擊。因為這些企業如果統治了未來的5G網絡，將給世界帶來不可接受的風險。」對索羅斯的批判，中國外交部發言人華春瑩2019年1月25日在例行記者會上說，「個別人發表顛倒黑白與是非的評論，毫無意義，不值一駁。在當今全球化不斷深入發展的時代，只有秉持發展的眼光、開放的胸襟、包容的態度，才能為自身發展以及國與國之間關係發展開闢更廣闊的空間。」"},{"pid":"f325dda01a30239db711adc5b5a933b3676e35fa","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9efa6db521f7a978f4c256381f95cfdd3aae58a8","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:24:16.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":"82f9c1aebbdf4fa0c62242210622625fe4795471","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:24:31.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":"d7a3ec11cfa433fc963bdd32c6763684a136ae7b","tid":1427210,"uid":209449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:24:42.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a08a11c7843bd58ddbc655d24d078df9cc32ef","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:24:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1bc5761f7e65b05cb3d4c61dd4b8a226baf637f6","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:24:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"611c3c3d0cbd32135f6d3e903c2ecba1086a92f8","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:25:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fefa4ed9ffcadb5796422e1ab6e446968fca5744","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:26:23.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"a8d5e215edb49a9fe61d01a9fae0b380d538ef97","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:30:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%91%E8%89%B2%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%2589%25B2%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%259C%259F%25E4%25B8%2589&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=31efa2b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%91%E8%89%B2%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%89</a>"},{"pid":"cea367d2b20f7dd9451f8b5a0d72eee260464b23","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:31:01.000Z","msg":"求高人指點"},{"pid":"b9e6f7d101afafcdd40f2669bf0cbf12be73f9ce","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:35:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3804406f5f97060b5fc03002d054114dbb24111b","tid":1427210,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:36:25.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n一齊上一齊落<br />\n香港人加油"}]}